instruction: Using the facts given, generate a story about a character.
input:
Name: Jane Smith
Gender: Female
Age: 32
Location: New York City
Occupation: Public Relations Officer
output: Jane Smith was a 32 year old woman, living in the bustling streets of New York City. She worked as a Public Relations Officer. Originally from the Midwest, she had moved to New York to pursue her dreams of working in the public relations industry. Despite the long hours and many challenges she faced, she was determined to make it. She often stayed late at the office, working hard and networking with influential people in the industry. She had found a community in the city and her days were spent finding new and creative ways to promote her clients. She always had her sights set on bigger and better things, and was determined to make her mark.
